      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-ready condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed to the highest standard: the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the VANOS unit has been overhauled with uprated seals. The suspension geometry remains precise with fresh bushings and OEM dampers, ensuring the chassis handles with factory-new stiffness. The paint depth is consistent across all panels with no evidence of respray or oxidation. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key example for the collector who demands technical perfection.",
